                        <span class="card-title">Alderman Garsheo "Gus" Black</span>
                        <p class="about-para left-align">Gus Black is a proud husband, father and businessman. 
                            He is a decorated 30 year Marine and combat veteran who has served in 
                            Desert Storm, Desert Shield, Afghanistan, and two combat tours of duty in 
                            Iraq. He is married to Oretha Black, who retired from the Marine Corps 
